headline: $111 Million Net-Leased Portfolio 68 DST Fully Subscribed as ExchangeRight Expands its REIT’s Acquisition Pipeline
summary: PASADENA, Calif., July 21, 2025--ExchangeRight fully subscribes $111M DST of 16 net-leased assets, supporting REIT pipeline and 5% monthly income for investors.
